{"tid":1483223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入維園啊 集會唔夠人啊","createTime":"2019-08-18T11:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T11:33:01.000Z","uid":84358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da3ff54492cbe848305f1a4650fbda8cfc584875","tid":1483223,"uid":84358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"唔好以為出面塞曬入面就夠人<br />\n唔夠人啊<br />\n快啲吹雞叫人入黎"},{"pid":"bd59c87e31f3492214b0a630774b34e0a4f61b55","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"823"},{"pid":"83de15e4b008f9e949fe9e7cd254e5b0ecfd4c6a","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:01:32.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"58f3b310a08840826a81b18fb165f2ea7fce1d59","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"787d45258444cfdf3a19f566a9b8237e6c1bd16c","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"7b8f20fa4d811f3da4f0d17e193ed9248a8d8b0a","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"5eb8cbcf4517cfa886a91de2406c708856f00e2e","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"f6e52bd752af5a5c3f3681c57a839741681b0e90","tid":1483223,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"麻煩你了<br />\n<br />\n係現場可唔可以幫手做人潮管制<br />\n係我地決定要無大台的<br />\n<br />\n1. 銅鑼灣站人: 落月台搭去天后出<br />\n2. 維園人: 走向維園銅鑼灣方向出口 比空間人入<br />\n3. 來緊的人: 炮台山天后站 入維園<br />\n4. 銅鑼灣人: 想入維園去行上告士打道天橋"},{"pid":"99b62d88ad392f98f12d90b0f86030bdb87a02d1","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"2c8ccd8771f28d0602af43f25c618276eab3d78f","tid":1483223,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"SoGO門口附近果幾條路其實塞左好多個鐘!<br />\n銅鑼灣地鐵站既人目前係入唔到去  又出唔到黎<br />\n如果未入維園既求大家唔好擔遮<br />\n左穿右插就可以殺出條路去維園<br />\n<br />\n我由四點係銅鑼灣sogo到維園果條路塞左三個鐘 <br />\n依家關遮殺出一條血路先可以到到維園<br />\n但結果維園原來好少人<br />\n個個塞哂係地鐵站附近<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好行去皇室堡 sogo個方向 <br />\n呢條街係對流緊<br />\n因為有好多人未去維園架<br />\n<br />\n維園目前其實好少人!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好怕淋雨  因為塞左咁耐  都因為個個都開遮"},{"pid":"ccdae09fbb366ff5cc8c3413c52a2a5d1b7ccc80","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"6472d9b931ff7d61d9ffa688a8cd774dd313efc4","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"a237fdf316962162216335bb78bd0fdce78b47b5","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"未迫爆維園<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈"},{"pid":"36f83b1c26f8962223c0fe4485988020122629cb","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"未迫爆維園<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈"},{"pid":"aec30a8f527d42d8fa8bbf5d2eb2c23f6524c7ac","tid":1483223,"uid":84358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06a974657f0693af25a3767c6b7340aca8575cde","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"未迫爆維園<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈"},{"pid":"64159d7a6d381c7af7fd6f32cbebb6aead1acba4","tid":1483223,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-